'''Institute of Archaeologists of Ireland''' ({{lang-ga|Institiúid Seandálaithe na hÉireann}}) is an [[Ireland|Irish]] archaeology organisation based in [[Dublin]], [[Ireland]]. Founded in [[Merrion Square]], Dublin in August 2001, the organisation represents archaeologists who are working throughout Ireland.<ref>{{cite web|title=IAI Three-Year Strategic Plan (2015-2018)|url=http://www.iai.ie/strategy/|website=iai.ie|accessdate=15 September 2016|quote=The Institute of Archaeologists of Ireland was established in August 2001.}}</ref>

